    public class MLNInferenceResultFileReaderOperator
extends MLNAbstractFileReaderOperator
    Describes an evidence file reader operator.

    Provides its superclass with file role information. The parent class (MLNAbstractFileReaderOperator) then creates output ports for all example set types required by the file role.

    Author:
    Yann Kiraly
